					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">In order to be as generic as possible, I think a public domain barebones graphic set should include:
<br />
<br />Solid block
<br />Ladder
<br />Semisolid block (i.e. ones you can jump through and land on top)
<br />Harmful block (i.e. spikes)
<br />Collectible A (i.e. coins)
<br />Collectible B (i.e. keys)
<br />Collectible C (i.e. powerups)
<br />1-up
<br />Door (the most generic "goal" I can think of)
<br />Up, Down, Left, Right Arrows
<br />Fontface (Numbers and uppercase letters as a bare minimum)
<br />
<br />That's for BG anyway. Let me think up some sprites...</div>

